This extension has only one functionality - to customize your new tab and turn it into something completely unique and amazing.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", you accept and agree to installing the Geometric Structures extension and setting Chromeâ„¢ New Tab Search to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your search engine to be powered by Bing.

Geometric structures consist of a dynamic wallpaper with various lines that dance around your desktop and create different structures and patterns on your new tab.

Our extension also includes a subtle search bar that fits the aesthetics of the new tab look. You also have an option to choose between light and dark themes and small settings where you can adjust the speed and amount of shapes that are moving around your new tab.
